rows.label: bf10220100_0010
rows.name: Huh?

rows.label: bf10220100_0020
rows.name: You guys...

rows.label: bf10220100_0030
rows.name: R-Rex...

rows.label: bf10220100_0040
rows.name:
Why're we all here?
I thought I was...

rows.label: bf10220100_0050
rows.name:
I merely wished to examine
the shapes of your hearts.

rows.label: bf10220100_0060
rows.name: That voice...!

rows.label: bf10220100_0070
rows.name: You're-!

rows.label: bf10220100_0080
rows.name:
My name is Klaus.
The creator of this world.

rows.label: bf10220100_0090
rows.name: I have watched over you all this time.

rows.label: bf10220100_0100
rows.name:
I have seen your thoughts. Your desires.
The things you have achieved.

rows.label: bf10220100_0110
rows.name: So you did that, just now?

rows.label: bf10220100_0120
rows.name: Yes. Those were not you.

rows.label: bf10220100_0130
rows.name: I wanted to see another form, another you.

rows.label: bf10220100_0140
rows.name: Our other selves?

rows.label: bf10220100_0150
rows.name:
You mean we're all thinking
stuff like that deep down?

rows.label: bf10220100_0160
rows.name: Was that how we really feel?

rows.label: bf10220100_0170
rows.name: Then you saw it too?

rows.label: bf10220100_0180
rows.name:
Looks like we were all shown
the same kind of stuff.

rows.label: bf10220100_0190
rows.name:
It creeped me out!
What're you trying to prove?

rows.label: bf10220100_0200
rows.name:
...Those were
the fears you harbor...

rows.label: bf10220100_0210
rows.name: I don't get it at all!

rows.label: bf10220100_0220
rows.name: What was your purpose in showing us this?

rows.label: bf10220100_0230
rows.name: Those were not pleasant visions to behold.

rows.label: bf10220100_0240
rows.name: My only purpose...was to find out...

rows.label: bf10220100_0250
rows.name: how mankind has changed...

rows.label: bf10220100_0260
rows.name: and where it is headed.

rows.label: bf10220100_0270
rows.name: And were you disappointed?

rows.label: bf10220100_0280
rows.name: No...

rows.label: bf10220100_0290
rows.name:
As you stand before me right now...
That is who you are.

rows.label: bf10220100_0300
rows.name: That is enough.

rows.label: bf10220100_0310
rows.name: I came here because I met Homura.

rows.label: bf10220100_0320
rows.name: Is this really Eden?

rows.label: bf10220100_0330
rows.name: Are you really...

rows.label: bf10220100_0340
rows.name: I will show you everything.

rows.label: bf10220100_0350
rows.name: Memories... Mine, and those of this planet.
